snippet.title: Amber Heard Reacts To Johnny Depp Loss In Court | The Gossipy
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Reacts To Johnny Depp Loss In Court | The Gossipy

Welcome toThe Gossipy. We make interesting videos about Hollywood in English. We give you a closer look in the lives of celebrities like Kanye West, Ed Sheeran, The Rock, Jay Z, Selena Gomez, Kylie Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Rihanna and 100s more.

Johnny Depp’s fans are rallying on social media to demand justice for Johnny after the celebrity suffered yet another major legal setback in his ongoing lcourt battle against ex-wife Amber Heard and the British tabloid The Sun.

In the meantime, Amber Heard is shading Johnny Depp hard on Instagram and the fans are absolutely furious. Will Johnny Depp ever be able to prove his innocence against Amber Heard?
